Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent in Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average cycle time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE when preceded by a rejection from ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total elapsed time from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to occur after any prior rejection activity (e.g., Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION, Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR, Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER, or Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER)
Metric: the average of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' or `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time for Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in variants that include multiple re-submission cycles
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from the previous Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in rework loops
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases that eventually lead to Payment Handled
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be performed after Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in variants ending without payment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time elapsed in Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE for cases with more than two submission-rejection cycles
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average cycle time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE compared to the cycle time of Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between consecutive occurrences of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in multi-rejection variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from the first event in the case to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in rejected-only variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases where approval was later revoked
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by MISSING followed by Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
